(145, 1, '2018-09-11 07:36:24', '2018-09-11 07:36:24', '<ul class="a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none">\r\n 	<li><span class="a-list-item"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-56" src="http://localhost/wordpressProject/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/piano2-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /> FULL SIZE KEYBOARD: A true full size 61 key keyboard piano with standard key sizes features LCD screen, record and playback functionality, 100 keyboard sounds 100 rhythms, and 50 demo songs </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class="a-list-item"> HEADPHONES: A set of high quality headphone are included within your digital piano package meaning letting musicians and leaners play comfortably without disturbing others </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class="a-list-item"> STOOL: A durable and sturdy padded stool accompanies your musical keyboard kit meaning you can play without discomfort for hours </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class="a-list-item"> STAND: Your keyboard package provides a strong and adjustable keyboard stand that is designed to hold your keyboard securely and adjust to musicians of all sizes </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class="a-list-item"> LEARNING AID 1: To start your beginner keyboard journey the RockJam 561 provides your with both access to 30 free songs on the Simply Piano app </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class="a-list-item"> LEARNING AID 2: Two months of Face to Face lessons are provided through Take Lesson so you can take your keyboard play to the next level </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class="a-list-item"> POWER SUPPLY: Unlike a number of keyboard kits the RockJam understand that electronic keyboards require electricity, therefore your power supply is included within this all in one package.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="https://www.amazon.com/RockJam-Electronic-Keyboard-SuperKit-Headphones/dp/B01AJJIQQQ">https://www.amazon.com/RockJam-Electronic-Keyboard-SuperKit-Headphones/dp/B01AJJIQQQ</a>', 'RockJam 61-Key Electronic Keyboard SuperKit with Stand, S